data.description: Newly Constructed home Built in 2023! True Single Level Living at it's finest! Enjoy a maintenance free lifestyle at Oakmont Heights in this beautiful patio home with TONS of builder upgrades! Located on a quiet cul de sac, this home features 2 bedrooms, a large flex space that is currently being used as a 3rd bedroom, laundry room and luxurious 9-foot ceilings with crown molding. This open concept floor plan includes a family room with fire place, dining room and kitchen with large island, stainless steel appliances, upgraded granite countertops and solid wood shaker cabinetry, LVP flooring, and upgraded lighting. The large master bedroom features a large upgraded walk-in shower with glass doors and 3 Shower heads!!! (2 can be used at a time). This home includes too many upgrades to list. HOA covers landscaping and snow removal (over 2"). Great Proximity to Oakmont Dining, The Oakmont Bakery, shopping and the US Open 2025! Easy access to PA Turnpike and Rte 28!
